reviewText: The songs and dances are uplifting and make it worthwhile to watch this down to earth heart-warming story of modern Indian youth.

Action, funny , father son bond tested when he falls in love without expecting to great music especially the love song on way to airport my favorite bollywood movie yet a must see I watch over and over
The pairing for this movie is superb. Songs are fair. Movie is good. Shipped and delivery was as expected.
